32
00:01:47,431 --> 00:01:52,756
This meeting was put together at the bequest of a state senator that represented the Belmont Watertown area.

33
00:01:53,336 --> 00:02:02,884
So the FAA was just listening to the request, and that's why they held the meeting, and it was scheduled with those parties involved, and the city of Medford really wasn't invited formally.

34
00:02:03,745 --> 00:02:07,849
But I did want to just come back to let you know what transpired during the meeting.

35
00:02:08,329 --> 00:02:18,698
Obviously, a lot of the CAC members, Logan has a community board as well as Massport, so the two separate community boards that meet regularly.

36
00:02:18,958 --> 00:02:23,182
And several of those members were in attendance during this meeting.

37
00:02:23,242 --> 00:02:24,984
